{"tid":2239584,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"小心KE 3335 同其車主","createTime":"2020-10-12T05:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T02:51:33.000Z","uid":164634,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c17c15963e6dbbff3c4437b57870f8db2a11691","tid":2239584,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:05:16.000Z","msg":"癡線 而家啲人真係惡 成個黑社會咁<br />\n<br />\n尋日中午時分係灣仔 大王東街<br />\n明明望住一家人泊完街車走<br />\n跟尾哩部KE3335 一野隊到前車一家人無哂位<br />\n前車示意佢話唔夠位 <br />\nKE3335 司機九秒九衝落車走去前車凶九佢<br />\n成街都望住個金毛肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗做乜九 <br />\n個feel好似突登逼到前車冇位 就落車屌人咁<br />\n<br />\n果時係街等緊位食野<br />\n見到哂<br />\n後來有幾隻狗黎左同車主問話<br />\n唔知係咪有人見到報左狗<br />\n<br />\n我驚影佢想比佢屌又無謂 所以冇圖<br />\n但各位小心哩部車 道路炸彈feel多...<br />\n又係Benz E class 黎 好深色既"},{"pid":"6cfc191490f768add3af83d6c410d1e3ebe1e310","tid":2239584,"uid":369306,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"打佢老母啦"},{"pid":"cff04d5086ba5030f3d779b23bb9e4f6f2d72b80","tid":2239584,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"泊街邊有話夠唔夠位<br />\n有一次我9手出返嚟都係咁"},{"pid":"59ee2695ace5d6a51aff551dc57b8c4bc4354c0e","tid":2239584,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"大家係街到行過佢架車果陣小心啲唔好刮到人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3e01df46dbfc6de70c09504de9ff493981fb1b","tid":2239584,"uid":186072,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"cff04d5086ba5030f3d779b23bb9e4f6f2d72b80","tid":2239584,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"泊街邊有話夠唔夠位<br />\n有一次我9手出返嚟都係咁"},"citedBy":1,"re